title: SOF Middle School Tour
desc: Intended for parents and children in the 5th grade of a  District 2 ?elementary school, or parents and children who reside in  District 2,  with children in a parochial or non- public school. ?The school tour is an opportunity to learn about our academic and extra-curricular programs, visit our facilities, and speak with current students and faculty members. ?Please note: 1 ticket per family.
